article.description: — Caleb Hollander and Nick Muszynski scored 17 points apiece as Belmont topped George Mason 77-67 on Friday.
article.headline: Hollander carries Belmont past George Mason 77-67
article.linkText: Hollander carries Belmont past George Mason 77-67
article.story: WASHINGTON -- — Caleb Hollander and Nick Muszynski scored 17 points apiece as Belmont topped George Mason 77-67 on Friday. Luke Smith added 16 points Grayson Murphy had 11 for Belmont (2-0). Jordan Miller had 19 points for the Patriots (1-1). Josh Oduro added 12 points and Javon Greene had 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
